which government regulatory agencies tell their regulated 
industries what they plan to do 
the notice adopted tuesday asked for facts and studies about the 
industry recommendations for new rules or changes in existing 
rules and recommendations for legislation 
it also sought comments on among other things rates and the 
possible regulation of rates quality of service competition and 
the desirability of a possible requirement that every community 
with cable service be assured that two companies would compete to 
offer it 
